  "detailed_description": "《英雄之旅》是一款适合摸鱼时玩的放置挂机类游戏，核心玩法就是打怪刷装备，穿更好的装备打更强的怪，体验爆极品装备的快感。<br><br>相对于其他挂机游戏，《英雄之旅》的旅途不是无尽的，也不会一关卡住好几天。玩家每次上线都能感受到战斗力提升，最终目标是战胜罪魂之塔500层首领。未来还会为想收集极品装备的玩家更新困难模式。<br><br>下面是游戏内功能概览，希望能帮助大家更好地体验游戏。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431490/extras/8062b21d1aeeda789637afe05b316f63.avif?t=1687244474\" width=600 height=334 /></span><br>游戏内的英雄会自动战斗，战胜10波小怪后可以挑战本关首领。战胜怪物有概率获得金币、装备、技能碎片、伙伴和钻石等。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >设置</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431490/extras/dd6ed3ff424739526e2cb9120d5f18b8.avif?t=1687244474\" width=600 height=466 /></span><br>可以关闭音乐、修改分辨率等。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >地图</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431490/extras/f17dc18d37fe74dca9b2ecb9e279da05.avif?t=1687244474\" width=600 height=232 /></span><br>战胜本关首领后可以进入到下张地图，越靠后的地图怪物等级越高，掉落的装备也越好。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >属性</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431490/extras/7409b96b75b736df072e3153aa7ae6ca.avif?t=1687244474\" width=600 height=458 /></span><br>角色升级后可以获得属性点，力量影响攻击力、体质影响生命值。伤害代表队伍整体的输出能力、坚韧代表队伍整体的防御能力。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >背包</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431490/extras/3bb44009aa780e438aabf7593307a59a.avif?t=1687244474\" width=600 height=476 /></span><br>背包内装备名字后面的数字代表如果你装备了这件装备，你的能力会变化多少，红色代表提升，绿色代表下降。+-代表提升伤害、降低坚韧，-+代表降低伤害、提升坚韧。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >强化</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431490/extras/ce64eaa5d37680323b08df28bcfd7853.avif?t=1687244474\" width=518 height=182 /></span><br>可以将不需要的装备熔炼获得强化石，运气好还会获得新的装备。使用强化石可以强化装备基础属性，更换装备保留强化等级。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >技能</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431490/extras/2cae1722774676f732d5155e33cc8cbc.avif?t=1687244474\" width=336 height=290 /></span><br>收集一定数量的技能碎片自动升级。可以配置两套技能（单体、群体），战斗中会根据敌人数量不同自动更换。每个技能有不同的释放概率，会优先释放靠上的技能。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >商店</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431490/extras/5c2f4ded9ae0bb732f3b3c9b90c0ce5e.avif?t=1687244474\" width=354 height=146 /></span><br>使用金币购买装备，价格越贵的商品获得高品质装备概率越高。如果大量购买经常提示“背包已满”，可以在设置中开启“购买后自动一键熔炼”。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >天赋</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431490/extras/ad122098a50c00c45cfc2d97d6493b7d.avif?t=1687244474\" width=500 height=234 /></span><br>角色升级后可以获得天赋点，你可以选择升级属性、伙伴或者技能。游戏满级为1000级，刚好可以全部点满。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >伙伴</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431490/extras/726c8ac7457842d6d6973e9fd2523944.avif?t=1687244474\" width=600 height=416 /></span><br>战斗胜利有概率获得伙伴，两个同名伙伴可以合成一个更高级别的伙伴。不同级别副属性不同，虽然主属性按照比例继承主角，但是可以自由分配属性点和配置技能。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >称号</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431490/extras/c94bce7934902b5a02a6ec078512908c.avif?t=1687244474\" width=426 height=278 /></span><br>完成对应任务可以解锁称号，称号附加的属性永久生效。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >图鉴</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431490/extras/295ab492f82e8caf0875352128083738.avif?t=1687244474\" width=600 height=202 /></span><br>获得新装备可以解锁图鉴，解锁数量越多属性加成越高。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挑战</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431490/extras/8c244ba6211f969b18242f12e7f02111.avif?t=1687244474\" width=600 height=384 /></span><br>战胜对应副本首领后可以获得金币、钻石、技能、伙伴等。每个副本每4小时增加一次挑战次数，最多保留20次。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >罪魂之塔</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431490/extras/6c1bed8a0221acae94a292e49a092b28.avif?t=1687244474\" width=452 height=348 /></span><br>罪魂之塔战斗胜利可以获得神器点和幸运值，幸运值越高获得的装备和伙伴品质越高。500层首领是整个游戏最难的关卡。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >神器</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431490/extras/3ffdd8124d1447bd5909cf7048be2f9d.avif?t=1687244474\" width=506 height=590 /></span><br>使用神器点可以解锁或升级神器，使用钻石可以重置所有神器。点击对应神器上的锁头图标可以锁定，避免被重置。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >竞技场</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431490/extras/acb9b9dfbea668a136874d01728bf31b.avif?t=1687244474\" width=600 height=322 /></span><br>挑战队伍胜利后可以获得圣火，可以将圣火供奉给女神获得属性值加成。每小时增加一次挑战次数，最多保留40次。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >铁匠铺</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431490/extras/c43c576200c079099a43cbef14de1a94.avif?t=1687244474\" width=594 height=356 /></span><br>在铁匠铺可以对仓库内的装备使用高级熔炼，高级熔炼不会失败。每4小时增加一次次数，最多保留20次。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >幻化</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431490/extras/500b3ded378dc4c69b8c8649030da20f.avif?t=1687244474\" width=600 height=440 /></span><br>到达70关后战斗胜利可以获得幻化币，使用幻化币解锁形象可以获得永久属性。<br><br>玩家交流QQ群: 746183884",
